@startuml
participant "Zigbee Sensor\n(End Device)" as Sensor
participant "Gateway\n(Zigbee Radio & Parser)" as GW_Z
participant "Gateway\n(Modbus Register Map)" as GW_M
participant "PLC / SCADA\n(Modbus Master)" as PLC

note over Sensor: Deep Sleep State

== Zigbee Push Cycle ==
Sensor -> Sensor: Wake Up
Sensor -> Sensor: Read Sensor
Sensor -> GW_Z: Transmit Payload
note over Sensor: Return to \n Deep Sleep

GW_Z -> GW_Z: Decrypt & Parse
GW_Z -> GW_M: Update Register

== Modbus Poll Cycle ==
loop Cyclic Polling
    PLC -> GW_M: Read Data Request
    GW_M -> PLC: Sensor Data Response
end
@enduml